author: Sharon westman
title: Sharon westman
text: I never liked salmon and my holistic dr. Re amended I try yours. I am hooked. Love that it comes in single serving . It comes in a great insulated box and is always frozen when it is delivered. Keep up the good work. I never new there could be such a difference in the taste of salmon. Never fishy taste or smell.love,love,love.
